data.description: If you're looking for the perfect home, look no further. Here is a dream garage, 1140 sq ft with oversize garage doors to fit your boat or large truck. This Garage is a 4-car garage, the 3rd stall is a tandem with a garage door to the back yard. We have extended the back patio for entertaining. This home is like new without the wait for new construction, in a family-friendly neighborhood, close to Lakeview Subdivision in Gretna. Less than 2 years old with window blinds, fencing, landscape, and expanded patio already completed. This beautiful 4 bed, 3 bath ranch has it all. The main level has carpet, hardwood, and tile floors, a tray ceiling, a formal dining room, and features a fireplace. Also on the main level are 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and laundry. The kitchen features tile floors, quartz counters, a tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, a breakfast nook, and a breakfast bar. The primary bedroom is located on the main level and features carpet floors, a tray ceiling, and a walk-in closet. The primary bedroom's attached bath includes tile floors, quartz counters, and a tiled shower. The finished lower level features a wet bar, 2 bedrooms, a full bath, a partially finished workout area, and a storage area. Outside you'll find a porch and patio overlooking the yard with a wrought iron fence. Exterior features include a lawn irrigation system. With an awesome school district and less than a mile from the new Gretna sports complex to be completed this year. Also, a new lake is to go in in the next couple of years. If you are a VA Member ask us about assuming our loan to keep a 3.25% interest rate.
